item.title: 【Requests】[REQ VID] - Alkaline Trio "This Addiction" Alternate Music Video
item.description: Hi there! I've been searching for an alternative music video for "This Addiction" by Alkaline Trio in the highest quality available (and without subtitles, which the only existence of this video i can find had baked into, however i can't seem to find it on YouTube anymore!). I've been searching everywhere for any information or links to said video in higher/highest quality for a couple of years now and was wondering if anyone on here would happen to know of its whereabouts!
